| JOURNEY-{{ number }}.PP-01 | {{ pp_01_description | default("First pain point") }} | {{ pp_01_score | default(2) }} | {{ pp_01_stage | default("Stage") }} | {{ pp_01_root_cause | default("Root cause") }} | {{ pp_01_opportunity | default("Opportunity") }} |

